 AI-Powered Real-Time Stock Market Analyzer

 Overview

The AI-Powered Real-Time Stock Market Analyzer is a Python-based application that fetches live stock market data, analyzes stock performance, and displays insights through an interactive Streamlit dashboard. It also generates AI-based market summaries to help users understand current market trends.

---

Features

- Fetches real-time stock data using Yahoo Finance
- Calculates daily stock returns
- Identifies Top Gainer and Top Loser
- Displays average closing prices
- Shows trading volume analysis
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard
- AI-generated market summary

---

Technologies Used

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Plotly
- Yahoo Finance (yfinance)
- Google Gemini AI
- VS Code

